                <head>102. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d102fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Council, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> Institutional Files
                        (H–Files), Box 107. Secret. The meeting took place in the White House
                        Situation Room. <persName corresp="#p_CJ_1">Carter</persName> wrote “Zbig,
                        J” in the upper right corner.</note>
                </head>
